NAME
    mod_perl_guide - The mod_perl Guide

SYNOPSIS
    Use your favorite Netscape Browser to read the guide after
    installing the package.

DESCRIPTION
    This is an HTML version of the mod_perl guide. You can also see
    the online version at http://perl.apache.org/guide . This
    include the PDF version as well.

    mod_perl project's home page: http://perl.apache.org

INSTALLATION
    The guide is gets installed just like any other Perl module:

      perl Makefile.PL
      make install

CORRECTIONS
    Corrections and suggestions are welcome. If you submit patches,
    please do that against the POD source files in the *src*
    directory. Please take the POD file, edit it and send it to me.

    This package doesn't include the up-to-date POD sources, since
    they get modified all the time. Please download the latest
    sources CVS snapshot from http://www.stason.org/guide-snapshots/
    .

    Thank you!

AUTHOR
    Stas Bekman <stas@stason.org>

SEE ALSO
    perl(1), mod_perl(1).

